query: INSERT INTO members (userId, membershipTier, isChild, photoConsent, smsConsent, liabilityWaiverSigned) SELECT u.id, 'bronze', false, false, false, false FROM users u LEFT JOIN members m ON u.id = m.userId WHERE (u.name = 'doublecranch2015' OR u.email LIKE '%doublecranch%') AND m.id IS NULL;
